name: Sky High (Jacketdude323)
description: A new game inspired by Flappy Bird and A Platformer, Introducing Sky High, a fun and simple little flappy-platformer game, I tried to make some music for this game, and it sounds both good and ear drum breaking. Since Pixel Game's Development has stopped, I decided to make a new game and I hope this game can be a great mildstone for my development hobby :)
